text: Learn the history of the RSAF. Must visit for aviation enthusiasta.
I enjoyed seeing the aircraft which defended Singapore, and the staff are friendly and helpful.
Place was pretty awesome, lots of model aircraft on show and lots to learn. Wld not recommend tho if ur not interested in mouldy military relics
Interesting museum and free of charge. The museum promotes singapore air force in an interactive way. There are some flight simulation games for visitors to play.
Not much stuff to see, quite remote place. But still ok for students or kids. Free entry btw.
